【编者按】新冠病毒给湖北乃至全国带来一场危机，黄冈是这场疫情的重灾区之一。
The new crown virus brings a crisis to Hubei and even to the whole country. Huanggang is one of the hardest hit areas of the epidemic.
在这场战役中，黄冈人经历了旁观-卷入-创伤-斗争-反思的过程。
In this battle, the Huanggang people experienced the process of watching-involved-traumatizing-fighting-introspection.
我们用亲历者日记连载的形式，试图纵深还原疫情侵袭下的黄冈这60天。
We tried to restore Huanggang to 60 days under the attack of the epidemic in the form of a diary series of relatives.
【郝诗光：江岸名都小区综合党支部书记，业委会副主任】1月26日 阴今天起床把各个新闻渠道的信息都梳理了一遍，事态比我想像的严重。
Hao Shi-guang: The secretary of the comprehensive Party branch of the Riverbank Famous District, the deputy director of the Industry Committee, got up today and combed the information from all the news channels.
武汉、鄂州、黄州“封城”之快之严出乎意料之外。
Wuhan, Huizhou, Huangzhou "closure" of the fast beyond expectations.
小区的江总准备往团风方向走，在道路卡口被拦住折返。
The district of the river is always ready to go toward the direction of the tour, at the intersection of the road was stopped and turned back.
微信群里还是各种奇谈怪调，无力纠缠，我也不多说了。
In the micro-letter group or a variety of strange talk, powerless entanglement, I do not say more.
下楼转了一下，发现3个门岗都是开放的。
A short walk down the stairs revealed that all three gates were open.
虽然“封城”已经过了多天，一些居民仍然没有养成戴口罩的习惯，一些人大包小包地往回运东西，看样子是在做持久战的准备。
Although more than a few days have passed since the closure of the city, some residents are still not in the habit of wearing masks, and some are shuttling back and forth in what appears to be a protracted war.
社区打电话来沟通了一些情况，通报一些数据，我们小区已有人出现在确诊及疑似的名单里，让我们做好应对准备。
The community called to communicate some information, some data, our community has appeared on the list of diagnosis and suspected, let us prepare for the response.
业委会的工作群里，我提出了主动封闭小区的想法。
In the working group of the industry committee, I put forward the idea of actively sealing off the community.
主要做法是：关闭黄州大道方向的两个侧门，只留西湖四路的门口出入。
The main approach is to close the Huangzhou Avenue direction of the two side doors, leaving only the four West Lake Road access.
即日起，小区的机动车许出不许进，回来的车辆一律停在小区外。
This day, the small area of motor vehicles are not allowed to enter, all vehicles back outside the residential area.
大家多数同意，也有提出不同意见的，上级没有说封闭小区，我们自己先封了？如何跟居民交待？在一线抗疫的机关工作人员辛苦了一天，不让他们的车子回小区，会不会让他们有想法？不过特殊时期，特殊手段，最后以少数服从多数的形式，通过。
Most people agree that there are also different views, the superior did not say that the closed community, we sealed it first? How to tell the residents? The staff of the first-line anti-epidemic agencies worked hard for a day to prevent their cars from returning to their neighborhoods.
当即同物业公司联系，要他们做好封闭准备，从下午2时起，小区正式封闭。
Immediately contact the property company, want them to prepare for closure, from 2 p.m. onwards, the community formally closed.
消息发布到业主群里后，并没有意料之中的反弹，估计高反弹期已经过了，大家已经接受了事实，并积极面对吧。
After the news was released to the owners, there was no expected rebound, estimated that the high rebound period has passed, everyone has accepted the facts, and actively face it.
2时，正式封闭。
Formally closed at 0200 hours.
我把自己小车打横作为路障，封住了黄州大道入口。
I used my car as a roadblock, blocking the entrance to Huangzhou Avenue.
中岗改以电子化值守为主，人力倾斜到西湖四路门。
Zhonggang to the electronic value of the main, human tilt to the West Lake Road door.
再次关照值守人员，要做好解释工作，避免跟业主发生冲突。
Once again take care of the guard, to do a good job of interpretation, to avoid conflict with the owner.
【孙璐：黄冈市黄州区四海社区网格员】1月26日今天是大年初二，新年没有假期。
Sun Lu: The Huangzhou District Huangzhou District Community Grid Wang Lu: January 26 today is New Year's Day, there is no holiday.
老公也接到了通知要回去工作，他在一个乡镇上班，他是党员，要上一线。
Husband also received notification to go back to work, he works in a township, he is a party member, to be on the front line.
这几天特别担心，害怕传染给女儿和婆婆，隔离住也不现实，虽然社区也想了办法，想去酒店订房间，让我们都住在外面。
These days special worry, fear of transmission to daughter and mother-in-law, isolation is not realistic, although the community also thought of ways to go to the hotel to make reservations, let us all live outside.
但是我们也都有家庭，酒店也被支援的医生住满了。
But we all have families, and the hotel is full of doctors.
现在让孩子和老人住一间房，我住一间房，吃饭分开吃，特殊时期还是得自己做好防护。
Now let the children and the old people live in a room, I live in a room, eat separate meals, or special period of their own protection.
爱心物资抵达黄冈已是半夜时分。
It was midnight when the supplies arrived in Huanggang.
龙振江供图【龙振江：志愿者】1月26日好事多磨。
Dragon Zhenjiang Feature Map [Longzhenjiang: Volunteer] January 26 Good things wear off.
在新冠疫情最紧张的时候，我四处寻找可用的防护物资，从中牵线搭桥，帮助最需要它们的医院或者其他机构代购；或者帮助捐赠者代购防护物资，运送给他们需要捐赠的对象，有时候会遇到各种困难。
At the height of the New Crown epidemic, I looked around for protective equipment to match and help buy from hospitals or other agencies that needed them most, or to help donors procure protective materials for those they needed to donate, sometimes with difficulties.
今天我去的地方比较多，一路去汉川、孝感、仙桃这几个地方，去甄别各种防护物资的真假，还有性价比。
Today, I went to more places, along the way to Hanchuan, filial piety, peach these places, to screen a variety of protection materials true and false, and cost-effective.
一路上困难也不少。
It was difficult all the way.
记得从汉川出发去仙桃已经傍晚了，距仙桃还有20多公里，我要找的一家医疗用品生产企业马上要下班了。
I remember it is evening since I set out for Xiantao from Hanchuan, more than 20 kilometers from Xiantao, and I'm looking for a medical supplies manufacturer who will be off duty soon.
我开着货车只用了10分钟快速赶到，可是对方说“不卖了”。
It only took me 10 minutes to get in my van, but the other guy said "No more."
太无力了，只能求人。
Too weak to ask.
拿出照片、证明给他看，表明我确实是捐赠的，不是留着卖的。
Show him a picture, show him that I did donate, not keep it for sale.
终于取得对方相信，从只肯卖我100件防护服，求到了1000件，然后再求到1万件以上，最后对方还给我送了几百件，一共买了12,000多件回来。
At last I was convinced that I could sell only 100 suits of protective clothing, get a thousand pieces, then ask for more than 10,000, and finally give me back a few hundred pieces, a total of more than 12,000 returned.
买完之后已经晚上12点多了，高速路口上不去了。
It's past 12: 00 p. m., so I can't go to the high-speed intersection.
又是各种求人，耗费了三个多小时，回到黄冈已经是半夜3点多。
It took more than three hours, and it was more than 3 o'clock in the middle of the night to return to Huanggang.
这批物资是黄冈市中心医院急需的物品。
The supplies were urgently needed at the Huanggang Central Hospital.
尽管很累，我还是第一时间送到医院。
Tired as I was, I got to the hospital the first time.
也有意外的收获。
There have also been windfalls.
今天，我的志愿者微信群由最初的2个迅速扩展成16个群，太多有爱心的人参与进来。
Today, my volunteer micro-group expanded rapidly from two to 16 groups, with too many caring people participating.
这些日子我遇到的人，百分之九十以上都是刚认识一天两天的，但大家像战友一样，为着“抗疫”这样同一个目标，做起事来都很爽快。
More than 90 percent of the people I meet these days have just met for a day or two, but everyone, like their comrades-in-arms, acts with alacrity in pursuit of the same goal of fighting the plague.
比如，我在群里扔一句“今晚差28万（元）”购买物资款，大家纷纷垫资或捐款，2小时就齐了。
For example, I threw a "280,000 yuan (US $) short of this evening" in the group to buy goods, everyone in advance or donated money, two hours to complete.
我们黄冈人从没有这么团结过！【梦轩：已愈新冠肺炎患者 】1月26日这两天，一直有难受的状态。
We Huanggang people have never been so united! "Dream Xuan: The new crown pneumonia patients" January 26 these two days, has been in a miserable state.
我是1月18日晚住进医院。
I was admitted to the hospital on the night of January 18.
20日开始，我出现呼吸困难、胸闷症状。
Starting on the 20th, I have breathing difficulties, chest tightness symptoms.
21日，我要靠一边吸氧一边勉强维持呼吸，完全不能翻身更不能起床。
On the 21st, I had to suck in oxygen while barely breathing, never turn over and never get up.
22日高烧并开始严重腹泻。
Fever 22 and began to have severe diarrhea.
但我还是尽量维持着一个好的心态。
But I try to keep a good attitude.
入住医院头几天，大家已经知道了武汉多人死亡的消息。
In the first few days of hospital stay, we have learned of the death of many people in Wuhan.
病房的几位病友也被恐惧笼罩，不是唉声叹气就是一声不发。
Several sick patients in the ward were also shrouded in fear, either sighing or not saying a word.
相比之下，我的心态相对比较平和。
In contrast, my mentality is relatively peaceful.
我跟大家聊天，想办法舒缓病房的气氛，希望她们心态乐观一些。
I chat with you, try to soothe the atmosphere in the ward, hope they are optimistic.
我也告诉大家，尽量想办法多吃饭，多喝水，这样才能加强营养吸收，增强自身免疫力。
I also told everyone, try to find ways to eat more, drink more water, so as to enhance the absorption of nutrients, enhance their immunity.
家里的年货：腊肉。
New Year's at home: bacon.
马亿 供图【马亿：浠水县汪岗镇，北京回乡白领】1月26日越来越多的村子和镇都被封闭，不准任何车辆出入，对本地的日常生活当然会有很大的影响。
It is indicated that more and more villages and towns in these area are closed to traffic which would certainly have a great impact on the daily life of these area.
就拿吃的来说，我家还算好的，年前爸妈从我家的小菜园摘回来很多青菜和萝卜，加上家里提前做好的一些腊鱼肉，所以暂时是没什么影响。
Take food, my family is good, my parents picked a lot of vegetables and turnips from my small garden, plus some meat cooked in advance, so temporarily no impact.
对于那些没有提前储备的人家来说，这两天恐怕有些难过。
I'm afraid these two days have been a little sad for those who don't have advance reserves.
还有倒垃圾的问题，街道上本来是有固定垃圾站，但是现在没人愿意出门，很多人家里的垃圾就堆在屋门外，没人来收。
There is the problem of emptying rubbish. There used to be a garbage dump on the street, but now no one wants to go out.
斜对面有一个小超市，过年本来是一年中生意最红火的时候。
There is a small supermarket diagonally opposite, the New Year was supposed to be the most prosperous time of the year.
店铺里面的各种拜年礼盒、烟酒、烟花爆竹都会从屋内摆到屋外。
All kinds of New Year's Eve gift boxes, cigarettes and alcohol, fireworks will be put out of the house.
但是今年，小超市也没有开门。
But this year, the small supermarket didn't open either.
像这样的店铺，基本都是做熟人生意，年前进的货有很大一部分都是为了应对春节的需求。
Such shops, are basically do acquaintances business, the forward of the goods are a large part of the Spring Festival in response to the demand.
就拿爆竹来说，在我们这一条街道和垸里一直就有相互串门的习俗，大年初一的早上要到所有街上和垸里的人家里拜年，被拜年的人家就得放一小挂鞭炮。
For example, firecrackers, in our street and land has been a cross-door customs, New Year's Day morning to all street and people's homes, people are on the New Year's Day, people have to put a small hanging firecracker.
据我之前每年跟我妈到小超市抬鞭炮的经验，每年大年初一一天，我家消耗的鞭炮应该在200挂左右。
According to my previous experience of carrying firecrackers to a small supermarket with my mother every year, on the first day of the New Year, my consumption of firecrackers should be about 200 hanging.
但今年取消了大年初一的串门，我家几乎没有买鞭炮。
But this year cancelled the first day of New Year's visit, my family almost did not buy firecrackers.
但是进货总是要提前的。
But the purchase is always ahead of time.
按照我家的这个数字大概可以估计，小超市肯定是进了不少类似的货。
According to this number of my family can be estimated, the small supermarket must be a lot of similar goods.
如果“封城”一直到元宵节之后，哪怕提前一点儿开放，想象得到，这么多年货肯定是不容易全数卖出的。
If the "closed city" until after the Lantern Festival, even a little bit in advance of the opening, imagine, so many years of goods are not easy to sell.
【李颖霞：山东支援黄冈护师】1月26日作为山东省首批支援武汉医疗队成员之一，我跟随团队于2020年1月25日乘专机到武汉，又经过两个小时的车程，凌晨三点到达我们支援的目的地黄冈市。
As one of the first members of Shandong Provincial Support Team for Wuhan on January 26, I took a special plane to Wuhan on January 25, 2020, and two hours' drive to Huanggang, our support destination.
作为重灾区，黄冈急需医务人员的支援。
As a disaster area, Huang Gang urgently needs medical support.
简单睡了几个小时。
Slept for a few hours.
今天任务比较琐碎，建群、分组，发培训资料、自学材料，整理防护用品等。
Today's task is more trivial, set up groups, distribution of training materials, self-learning materials, finishing protective equipment.
我们医疗队成员共135人，分为普通患者救治组和重症患者救治组，我属于重症组。
There were 135 members of our medical team, divided into general patient treatment group and severe patients treatment group, I belong to the severe group.
可能面临的是最危重、工作量最大的患者。
It is likely to be the most critical and work-intensive patients.
作为一名曾经在重症医学科工作了12年的重症专科护士，我有信心有把握把病人护理好！下午各组组长开会，跟黄冈市卫计委负责人见面，对工作进行了分配，我们被分配在黄冈市传染病医院，估计也是黄冈市收治肺炎病人最多最重的医院。
As an intensive care specialist who has worked in intensive care for 12 years, I am confident that I can take good care of my patients! In the afternoon, the group leaders met with the head of the Huanggang Municipal Health and Planning Commission and distributed the work.
自从报名来湖北那一刻起，说实在的，我心里一直没有犹豫、担心、害怕过，因为我知道，作为一名工作25年的老护理人，我有信心、有能力、有专业的知识来做好自我防护，同时能够护理好每一位病人。
From the moment I signed up for Hubei, I had not hesitated, worried or feared, for I knew that, as an old caregiver for 25 years, I had the confidence, ability and professional knowledge to protect myself and care for every patient.
相信我们很快就会打赢这场没有硝烟的战争。
I believe we shall soon win the war without the smoke.
吃完午饭我爸想出去透透气，被我妈拉住了。
After lunch my father wanted to go out for a breath and was held by my mother.
